                    <p class="mt-4 text-body-md text-gray-800">
                        We launched our app in the autumn of 2021 and I honestly cannot understand how we could
                        run our business
                        beforehand. With the app, communication has not only become easier, but it has also been
                        strengthened
                        both within individual hotels and across the company.
                    </p>
